HEADWORD: Midfeather
<hw>Mid"feath`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Steam Boilers)</fld> <def>A vertical water space in a fire box or
combustion chamber.</def>⟦br⟧
